column2: SELECT TOP # dbo.fCosmoDl(s.z) AS Dl,      p.petroMag_r,      p.extinction_r,     s.z,      p.petroMag_r-#*log1#(dbo.fCosmoDl(s.z))#-extinction_r AS absmag FROM  SpecObj AS s     INNER JOIN PhotoObj AS p     ON s.bestObjID=p.objID WHERE SpecClass=# AND s.z># AND s.z<# AND p.petroMag_r># ) SELECT FLOOR(absmag/#)*# AS AbsMag,      COUNT(*) as Gyakorisag FROM q WHERE absmag<# AND z<# GROUP BY FLOOR(absmag/#)*#
